os_mock.path.abspath = os.path.abspath
os_mock.path.join = os.path.join
os_mock.path.exists.return_value = True
os_mock.listdir.side_effect = [['a.primitive.json',
    'another.primitive.json', 'some'], ['other'], ['primitive.json']]
os_mock.path.isdir.return_value = False
os_mock.path.isdir.side_effect = [False, False, True, True, False]
annotations = discovery._search_annotations('/path/to', 'other')
assert annotations == {'/path/to/another.primitive.json':
    'another.primitive', '/path/to/some/other/primitive.json':
    'some.other.primitive'}
patch('mlblocks.discovery.os')
